@node "Features" "Featuresáá"
 
 @{b}THE FEATURES@{ub}
 
 À Relative Conferences
 À Password protection of any conference
 À Fast Join support `>` `<`
 À Full cursor support
 À Ability to drop carrier after conference password hack
 À Use of the internal conference list
 
 À and even many more...
@endnode

